headline: Del Webb Announces Grand Opening of New Greater Palm Springs Community, Desert Retreat
summary: PALM SPRINGS, Calif., November 13, 2025--Del Webb, the nation’s leading builder of active-adult communities for those 55 and older, today announced the grand opening of its newest community, Del Webb Desert Retreat. A Grand Opening event will take place on Saturday, November 15th from 10 AM to 2 PM.
